<div class="day-section">
<div class="day-title">第4天（D4）：流程控制全解</div>
<div class="day-meta">预计3h理论 + 2h实践 | <span class="tag tag-fe">前端：对比JS switch的break穿透</span></div>

<h4>知识点</h4>
<p><code>if-else</code> 嵌套不超过3层为宜。<code>switch</code> 在Java 12+支持箭头语法（无需break），支持 <code>yield</code> 返回值。<code>for</code> 循环三种形式：计数for、条件while、集合for-each。<code>break</code> 跳出当前循环，<code>continue</code> 跳过本次迭代，带标签的 <code>break label;</code> 可跳出多层循环。</p>

<h4>可运行代码示例</h4>
<pre><code class="java">package com.example.day04;

import java.util.Scanner;

public class ATMSystem {
    private static double balance = 1000.0;
    
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        boolean running = true;
        
        while (running) {
            System.out.println("\n=== ATM系统 ===");
            System.out.println("1.查询余额 2.存款 3.取款 4.退出");
            System.out.print("请选择: ");
            int choice = sc.nextInt();
            
            switch (choice) {
                case 1 -> System.out.println("余额: " + balance);
                case 2 -> {
                    System.out.print("存款金额: ");
                    double amount = sc.nextDouble();
                    if (amount > 0) {
                        balance += amount;
                        System.out.println("存款成功");
                    } else {
                        System.out.println("金额无效");
                    }
                }
                case 3 -> {
                    System.out.print("取款金额: ");
                    double amount = sc.nextDouble();
                    if (amount > 0 && amount <= balance) {
                        balance -= amount;
                        System.out.println("取款成功");
                    } else {
                        System.out.println("余额不足或金额无效");
                    }
                }
                case 4 -> {
                    System.out.println("感谢使用，再见！");
                    running = false;
                }
                default -> System.out.println("无效选项");
            }
        }
        sc.close();
    }
}
