<div class="day-title">第19天（D19）：HashMap与Set</div>
<div class="day-meta">预计3h理论 + 2h实践 | <span class="tag tag-fe">前端：对比JS Map/Set</span></div>

<h4>知识点</h4>
<p><strong>HashMap</strong>底层是数组+链表+红黑树（Java 8+）。当链表长度≥8且数组长度≥64时转红黑树。<code>hashCode()</code>决定桶位置，<code>equals()</code>决定键是否相等。</p>

<h4>可运行代码示例</h4>
<pre><code class="java">package com.example.day19;

import java.util.*;

public class MapDemo {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Map&lt;String, Integer&gt; scores = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();
        scores.put("张三", 90); scores.put("李四", 85); scores.put("王五", 92);
        
        scores.forEach((k, v) -> System.out.println(k + " -> " + v));
        
        scores.computeIfAbsent("赵六", k -> 88);
        scores.merge("张三", 5, Integer::sum);
        
        Map&lt;String, String&gt; cache = new LinkedHashMap&lt;&gt;(16, 0.75f, true) {
            @Override
            protected boolean removeEldestEntry(Map.Entry&lt;String, String&gt; eldest) {
                return size() &gt; 3;
            }
        };
        cache.put("A", "1"); cache.put("B", "2");
        cache.put("C", "3"); cache.get("A");
        cache.put("D", "4");
        System.out.println("LRU缓存: " + cache.keySet());
        
