<div class="day-section">
<div class="day-title">第23天（D23）：线程基础与同步</div>
<div class="day-meta">预计3h理论 + 2h实践 | <span class="tag tag-fe">前端：对比JS单线程事件循环</span></div>

<h4>知识点</h4>
<p>Java中创建线程两种方式：继承 <code>Thread</code> 或实现 <code>Runnable</code>（推荐）。线程状态：NEW→RUNNABLE→BLOCKED/WAITING/TIMED_WAITING→TERMINATED。<strong>synchronized</strong> 可修饰方法或代码块，底层通过monitor实现互斥。</p>

<h4>可运行代码示例</h4>
<pre><code class="java">package com.example.day23;

public class ThreadSync {
    private int tickets = 100;
    
    // 同步方法
    public synchronized boolean sellTicket() {
        if (tickets &gt; 0) {
            System.out.println(Thread.currentThread().getName() + " 售出 " + tickets--);
            return true;
        }
        return false;
    }
    
    // 同步代码块（更细粒度）
    public void sellTicketBlock() {
        synchronized (this) {
            if (tickets &gt; 0) {
                System.out.println(Thread.currentThread().getName() + " 售出 " + tickets--);
            }
        }
    }
    
    public static void main(String[] args) throws InterruptedException {
        ThreadSync station = new ThreadSync();
        
        Runnable task = () -> {
            while (station.sellTicket()) {
                try { Thread.sleep(10); } catch (InterruptedException e) { break; }
            }
        };
        
        Thread t1 = new Thread(task, "窗口1");
        Thread t2 = new Thread(task, "窗口2");
        Thread t3 = new Thread(task, "窗口3");
        
        t1.start(); t2.start(); t3.start();
        t1.join(); t2.join(); t3.join();
        System.out.println("售票结束，剩余: " + station.tickets);
    }
}
</code></pre>

<h4>练习任务</h4>
