<div class="day-section">
<div class="day-title">第24天（D24）：线程池与异步</div>
<div class="day-meta">预计3h理论 + 2h实践</div>

<h4>知识点</h4>
<p><strong>线程池</strong>通过复用线程降低创建销毁开销。核心参数：corePoolSize、maximumPoolSize、keepAliveTime、workQueue、rejectedExecutionHandler。<strong>CompletableFuture</strong>是Java 8引入的异步编程工具，支持链式组合、异常处理、并行执行。</p>

<h4>可运行代码示例</h4>
<pre><code class="java">package com.example.day24;

import java.util.concurrent.*;
import java.util.List;
import java.util.Arrays;

public class ThreadPoolDemo {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {
        // 自定义线程池
        ThreadPoolExecutor executor = new ThreadPoolExecutor(
            2, 4, 60L, TimeUnit.SECONDS,
            new LinkedBlockingQueue&lt;&gt;(100),
            new ThreadFactory() {
                int count = 0;
                public Thread newThread(Runnable r) {
                    return new Thread(r, "worker-" + (++count));
                }
            },
            new ThreadPoolExecutor.CallerRunsPolicy()
        );
        
        // 批量提交Callable任务
        List&lt;Future&lt;String&gt;&gt; futures = executor.invokeAll(Arrays.asList(
            () -> { Thread.sleep(500); return "任务A完成"; },
            () -> { Thread.sleep(300); return "任务B完成"; },
            () -> { Thread.sleep(800); return "任务C完成"; }
        ));
        
        for (Future&lt;String&gt; f : futures) {
            System.out.println(f.get());
        }
        
        // CompletableFuture异步链
        CompletableFuture.supplyAsync(() -> fetchOrder(1001L), executor)
            .thenApply(order -> calculatePrice(order))
            .thenAccept(price -> System.out.println("最终价格: " + price))
            .exceptionally(ex -> { System.err.println("错误: " + ex.getMessage()); return null; })
            .join();
        
        executor.shutdown();
    }
    
    static String fetchOrder(Long id) {
        System.out.println(Thread.currentThread().getName() + " 查询订单");
        return "Order{" + id + "}";
    }
    
    static double calculatePrice(String order) {
        return 199.99;
    }
}
</code></pre>

