<h4>知识点</h4>
<p><strong>JOIN</strong>：INNER JOIN取交集，LEFT JOIN保留左表全部，RIGHT JOIN保留右表全部。<strong>子查询</strong>可分为相关子查询（慢）和非相关子查询。<strong>窗口函数</strong>（ROW_NUMBER/RANK/LAG/LEAD）在MySQL 8.0+支持。<strong>执行计划</strong>看type列：system > const > eq_ref > ref > range > index > ALL。</p>

<h4>可运行代码示例（SQL）</h4>
<pre><code class="sql">-- 查询每个用户最新订单
SELECT o.*
FROM orders o
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT user_id, MAX(created_at) AS max_time
    FROM orders
    GROUP BY user_id
) latest ON o.user_id = latest.user_id AND o.created_at = latest.max_time;

-- 销售排行（窗口函数）
SELECT 
    product_id,
    SUM(quantity) AS total_qty,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY SUM(quantity) DESC) AS sales_rank
FROM order_items
GROUP BY product_id;

-- 用户消费分层
SELECT 
    u.username,
    COUNT(o.id) AS order_count,
    COALESCE(SUM(o.total_amount), 0) AS total_spent,
    CASE 
        WHEN SUM(o.total_amount) &gt; 10000 THEN 'VIP'
        WHEN SUM(o.total_amount) &gt; 5000 THEN '高级'
        ELSE '普通'
    END AS level
FROM users u
LEFT JOIN orders o ON u.id = o.user_id
GROUP BY u.id, u.username;
</code></pre>

