<div class="day-section">
<div class="day-title">第36天（D36）：MyBatis入门</div>
<div class="day-meta">预计3h理论 + 2h实践 | <span class="tag tag-fe">前端：对比ORM vs 手写SQL</span></div>

<h4>知识点</h4>
<p><strong>MyBatis</strong>是半自动ORM框架，相比JPA更灵活，适合复杂SQL场景。核心组件：<strong>SqlSessionFactory</strong>、<strong>Mapper接口</strong>（绑定XML或注解）。Spring Boot通过 <code>mybatis-spring-boot-starter</code> 自动整合。</p>

<h4>可运行代码示例</h4>
<pre><code class="java">package com.example.demo.mapper;

import com.example.demo.entity.UserEntity;
import org.apache.ibatis.annotations.*;
import java.util.List;

@Mapper
public interface UserMapper {
    
    @Select("SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = #{id}")
    @Results({
        @Result(property = "createdAt", column = "created_at")
    })
    UserEntity findById(Long id);
    
    @Select("&lt;script&gt;SELECT * FROM users WHERE 1=1"
        + "&lt;if test='username != null'&gt; AND username LIKE CONCAT('%', #{username}, '%')&lt;/if&gt;"
        + "&lt;if test='email != null'&gt; AND email = #{email}&lt;/if&gt;"
        + "&lt;/script&gt;")
    List&lt;UserEntity&gt; search(@Param("username") String username, @Param("email") String email);
    
    @Insert("INSERT INTO users(username, email, created_at) VALUES(#{username}, #{email}, NOW())")
    @Options(useGeneratedKeys = true, keyProperty = "id")
    int insert(UserEntity user);
    
    @Update("UPDATE users SET username=#{username}, email=#{email} WHERE id=#{id}")
    int update(UserEntity user);
    
    @Delete("DELETE FROM users WHERE id = #{id}")
    int deleteById(Long id);
}
</code></pre>

<h4>练习任务</h4>
<ol>
<li>将第35天博客系统的JPA Repository全部替换为MyBatis Mapper。</li>
<li>对比同一条查询在JPA和MyBatis下的SQL输出差异。</li>
</ol>
</div>

