<h4>知识点</h4>
<p>MyBatis XML映射文件中，<code>&lt;if&gt;</code>条件判断、<code>&lt;where&gt;</code>自动处理AND/OR、<code>&lt;foreach&gt;</code>循环（用于IN语句）、<code>&lt;choose&gt;/&lt;when&gt;/&lt;otherwise&gt;</code>多分支。<strong>PageHelper</strong>是MyBatis分页插件，通过 <code>PageHelper.startPage(page, size)</code> 实现物理分页。</p>

<h4>可运行代码示例（XML）</h4>
<pre><code class="xml">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?&gt;
&lt;!DOCTYPE mapper PUBLIC "-//mybatis.org//DTD Mapper 3.0//EN"
  "http://mybatis.org/dtd/mybatis-3-mapper.dtd"&gt;
&lt;mapper namespace="com.example.demo.mapper.ArticleMapper"&gt;

    &lt;resultMap id="articleMap" type="com.example.demo.entity.Article"&gt;
        &lt;id property="id" column="id"/&gt;
        &lt;result property="title" column="title"/&gt;
        &lt;association property="author" javaType="com.example.demo.entity.UserEntity"&gt;
            &lt;id property="id" column="author_id"/&gt;
            &lt;result property="username" column="author_name"/&gt;
        &lt;/association&gt;
        &lt;collection property="tags" ofType="com.example.demo.entity.Tag"&gt;
            &lt;id property="id" column="tag_id"/&gt;
            &lt;result property="name" column="tag_name"/&gt;
        &lt;/collection&gt;
    &lt;/resultMap&gt;

    &lt;select id="searchArticles" resultMap="articleMap"&gt;
        SELECT a.*, u.id as author_id, u.username as author_name,
               t.id as tag_id, t.name as tag_name
        FROM articles a
        LEFT JOIN users u ON a.author_id = u.id
        LEFT JOIN article_tags at ON a.id = at.article_id
        LEFT JOIN tags t ON at.tag_id = t.id
        &lt;where&gt;
            &lt;if test="keyword != null and keyword != ''"&gt;
                AND a.title LIKE CONCAT('%', #{keyword}, '%')
            &lt;/if&gt;
            &lt;if test="authorId != null"&gt;
                AND a.author_id = #{authorId}
            &lt;/if&gt;
            &lt;if test="tagIds != null and tagIds.size() &gt; 0"&gt;
                AND a.id IN (
                    SELECT article_id FROM article_tags
                    WHERE tag_id IN
                    &lt;foreach collection="tagIds" item="id" open="(" separator="," close=")"&gt;
                        #{id}
                    &lt;/foreach&gt;
                )
            &lt;/if&gt;
        &lt;/where&gt;
        ORDER BY a.created_at DESC
    &lt;/select&gt;
&lt;/mapper&gt;
